=== Components ===
* [[../wiki2html.awk|wiki2html.awk]]: text prozessor
* [[../wiki.cgi|wiki.cgi]]: symlink to wiki2html.awk

==== Optional ====
* [[../wiki.css|wiki.css]]: Stylesheet
* header: <span style='color:red'>TODO</span>
* footer: <span style='color:red'>TODO</span>

=== Limits ===
The page name must be between 3 and 32 characters long. They can contain letters (A-Z, a-z), numbers (0-9) or underscores (_).

=== Syntax ===
compatible to the MediaWiki-Textformat <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Formatting</ref> and/or partially to MoinMoin <ref>http://moinmo.in/</ref>

{|
 ! colspan=2 | Creole <ref>http://www.wikicreole.org/wiki/Creole1.0#section-Creole1.0-Headings</ref> & MediaWiki <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Formatting</ref> Headings
 |-
 | {{{ = Head 1 = }}}                         || <h1>Head 1</h1>
 |-
 | {{{ == Head 2 == }}}                       || <h2>Head 2</h2>
 |-
 | {{{ === Head 3 === }}}                     || <h3>Head 3</h3>
 |-
 | {{{ ==== Head 4 ==== }}}                   || <h4>Head 4</h4>
 |-
 | {{{ ===== Head 5 ===== }}}                 || <h5>Head 5</h5>
 |-
 | {{{ ====== Head 6 ====== }}}               || <h6>Head 6</h6>
 |-
 | {{{ === not **bold** or //italic// === }}}         
 |
=== not **bold** or //italic// ===
 |-
 ! colspan=2 | Creole <ref>http://www.wikicreole.org/wiki/Creole1.0#section-Creole1.0-BoldAndItalics</ref> text formating
 |-
 | {{{ **bold** }}}                           || **bold**
 |-
 | {{{ //italic// }}}                         || //italic//
 |-
 | {{{  **//bold and italic//** }}}           || **//bold and italic//**
 |-
 | {{{  //**italic and bold**// }}}           || //**italic and bold**//
 |-
 | {{{  **bold** or //italic// }}}            || **bold** or //italic//
 |-
 | {{{  //italic// or **bold**  }}}           || //italic// or **bold**
 |-
 | {{{  //** not italic and not bold //** }}} || //** not italic and not bold //**
 |-
 | {{{  **// not bold and not italic **// }}} || **// not bold and not italic **//
 |-
 ! colspan=2 | MediaWiki <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Formatting</ref> text formating
 |-
 | <nowiki> ''italic'' </nowiki>                         ||''italic''
 |-
 | <nowiki> '''bold''' </nowiki>                         ||'''bold'''
 |-
 | <nowiki> '''''bold & italic''''' </nowiki>            ||'''''bold & italic''''' 
 |-
 ! colspan=2 | Creole <ref>http://www.wikicreole.org/wiki/Creole1.0#section-Creole1.0-HorizontalRule</ref> & MediaWiki <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Formatting</ref> horizontal rule
 |-
 | {{{ ---- }}}
 |
----
 |-
 ! colspan=2 | Creole <ref>http://www.wikicreole.org/wiki/Creole1.0#section-Creole1.0-Lists</ref> & Mediawiki <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Formatting</ref> lists 
 |-
 |
 # numbered item 1
 # numbered item 2
 ## numbered sub item 2.1
 ## numbered sub item 2.2
 # numbered item 3
 |
# numbered item 1
# numbered item 2
## numbered sub item 2.1
## numbered sub item 2.2
# numbered item 3
 |-
 |
 * unnumbered item 1
 * unnumbered item 2
 ** unnumbered sub item 2.1
 ** unnumbered sub item 2.2
 * unnumbered item 3
 |
* unnumbered item 1
* unnumbered item 2
** unnumbered sub item 2.1
** unnumbered sub item 2.2
* unnumbered item 3
 |
 |-
 ! colspan=2 | MediaWiki <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Formatting</ref> Definition and mixed lists
 |-
 |
 ; title
 : definition 1
 : definition 2
 :: definition 2.1
 |
; title
: definition 1
: definition 2
:: definition 2.1
 |-
 |
 * unnumbered item 1
 * unnumbered item 2
 *# sub item * #
 #* sub item # *
 * unnumbered item 3
 |
* unnumbered item 1
* unnumbered item 2
*# sub item * #
#* sub item # *
* unnumbered item 3
 |-
 ! colspan=2 | Creole <ref>http://www.wikicreole.org/wiki/Creole1.0#section-Creole1.0-NowikiPreformatted</ref> preformatted text
 |-
 |
<pre>{{{
 not //italic// formated by wiki
 not <i>italic</i> formated by html
 not a [[#anchor]]
}}}</pre>
 |
{{{
 not //italic// formated by wiki
 not <i>italic</i> formated by html
 not a [[#anchor]]
}}}
 |-
 ! colspan=2 | MediaWiki <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Formatting</ref> Preformatted text
 |-
 |
<pre>
 ''italic'' formated by wiki
 <i>italic</i> formated by html
 [[#anchor]]
</pre>
 |
 ''italic'' formated by wiki
 <i>italic</i> formated by html
 [[#anchor]]
 |-
 ! colspan=2 | MediaWiki <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Formatting#HTML</ref> HTML Preformatted text
 |-
 | {{{ <tt>Fixed width text</tt> }}} || <tt>Fixed width text</tt>
 |-
 | {{{ <code>source code</code> }}}  || <code>source code</code>
 |-
 |
{{{
<pre>
not ''italic'' formated by wiki
not <i>italic</i> formated by html
not [[#anchor]]
</pre>
}}}
 |
<pre>
not ''italic'' formated by wiki
not <i>italic</i> formated by html
not [[#anchor]]
</pre>
 |-
 ! colspan=2 | Creole <ref>http://www.wikicreole.org/wiki/Creole1.0#section-Creole1.0-LinksInternalExternalAndInterwiki</ref> & MediaWiki <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Links</ref> Links 
 |-
 | <nowiki>[[#internal anchor]]</nowiki> || [[#internal anchor]]
 |-
 | <nowiki>internal [[link]] to other wiki page</nowiki>
 | internal [[link]] to other wiki page
 |-
 | <nowiki>piped link [[link|with different text]]</nowiki>
 | piped link [[link|with different text]]
 |-
 | <nowiki>external link http://www.mediawiki.org</nowiki>
 | external link http://www.mediawiki.org
 |-
 ! colspan=2 | MediaWiki <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Links#External_links</ref> external links 
 |-
 | <nowiki>external link [http://www.mediawiki.org with different text]</nowiki><ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Links#External_links</ref>
 | external link [http://www.mediawiki.org with different text]
 |-
 | <nowiki>external link numbered [http://www.kernel.org]</nowiki><ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Links#External_links</ref>
 | external link numbered [http://www.kernel.org]
 |-
 ! colspan=2 | HTML links
 |-
 | <nowiki>HTML link <a href="http://www.mediawiki.org">MediaWiki</a></nowiki>
 | HTML link <a href="http://www.mediawiki.org">MediaWiki</a>
 |-
