|Cell A1        |Two lines\\in Cell B1  |
|Cell A2        |Cell B2                |
 |-
 ! colspan=2 | MediaWiki <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Tables</ref> tables
 |-
 |
<pre>
{|
! Head A 
! Head B 
|-
| Cell A1
| Cell B1
|-
| Cell A2
| Cell B2
|}
</pre>
